Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote this question down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've also provided your wife, Susan, a copy of this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that the basic needs of food, clothing, and shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and self-actualization must be achieved by 80% of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,before humanity could calculate between 500 and 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This would still require the mind and ego to achieve these basic needs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the daily lives of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual level of consciousness where love is the essence of human behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,could provide the paradigm shift into the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which comes first, the chicken or the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does humanity reach a balance between basic needs and spiritual enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know, now that you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were born into the optimum opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant by instant, we make choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By so doing, we transcend past karma
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and move into, out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,force, into power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, whereas at one level, we have to kill somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to get his wife and his crop and his money
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and tear off his jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all that comes to us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with no energy and no effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a loving wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,People give you gifts right and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You suffer from the problem of abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the automatic consequence of that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the way the field reacts to what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have become, then, is magnetic to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the field can't do enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be careful not to say anything I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I mention that I like licorice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,within a week, I'll get tons of licorice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,packages of licorice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,licorice stuff by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At a lower level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're wanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because of your wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you deny it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when you let go of wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that abundance happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there are many workshops
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to increase prosperity and such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say wanting prosperity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the very thing that keeps it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing to do is to find satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in being that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best that you can be what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is being what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Class, to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is the waiter that serves with style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that is a waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The chef who does it with finesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The cook, the cleaning lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the taxi cab driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,whose friendlies all get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,goes out of his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is being what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you pull to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,self-abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The classy cab driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gets heavy tips all the time, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The great waitress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hi, Gertrude,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sit in Gertrude's side of the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the world seeks you out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because of what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you've become,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we just covered on one of those slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gracious, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,saying, gee, thanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that was terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't take a great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn your life from wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't take a great deal to turn your life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And, as I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem of abundance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I give workshops on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how to handle the problem of abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you put it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that offers us the maximum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunity to grow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which we become
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,attracts to it all the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the other end of the scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we repel all the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We repel all the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We repel all the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We repel all the good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,repel all the good things. A decent couple goes to look at an apartment in a neighborhood covered
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with filth. It says, no thank you. Repelled by the negative. So we become our potentiality and as a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence, the field responds to us. We find fulfillment then in every moment of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that we do. Everything that we do. When I was a cab driver, I made more money than a cab driver
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,per mile in the company. When I was a bartender, I doubled the business. Everything I did, I did
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,with, I love doing it and I'm right. I knew every address, which side of the street, 2262 North
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tulsa. I knew it was this side or the right side. I knew all the one-way streets so you could come
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,around this way. You know what I mean? You just try to be the best you can at everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we get 80% of the world's population to be that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get 80% of the world's population anyway. Why? Because this is the optimum,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,environment. See, a lot of people want to turn this into a celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a celestial realm. That's supposed to be a celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be where you have the choices all the way from the cutthroat at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to a Christ-like figure at the top. This is purgatorial in a way because it covers the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,whole spectrum. If you go to a celestial realm, you're talking about 500 and up, 540 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any choices there. You don't have a choice between
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,falling for this and falling for that. So this is a world of maximum opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire to change it. It's perfectly fine the way it is because it offers us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody who calibrates 120 or, well, let's say 120. Where is he going to get reborn and move
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,from 120 up to 350? Where are you going to get born? Not in the celestial realm. Not in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,either. You know, you can't move out. You know, you've got to move out. You've got to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be in a place with absolute opportunity and freedom. Here you can curse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the guy who pulls in front of you in traffic or say, I'll give the guy a break. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that whole choice. In heaven, you don't have that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all flowers and celestial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A golden fairy flows in front of you and you swing in your celestial gondola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got to have the opportunity to curse him or give him the okay. So this is the,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to me, the world of maximum spiritual opportunity. So we value the diversity here. We value the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,diversity because of the tremendous opportunity. Here you can jump 100. I've had people in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in a group like this, jump 150 right there in the lecture, you know, 150 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the equivalent of 25 lifetimes or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you for that distinction. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have questions, if you would line up over here and then we'll take those one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have books to sign, if you'd also queue up over there, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you have books to sign, I'll be happy to sign them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't think I was going to have less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no books to sign and I have a simple technical question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your works, I've been meditating for the past nine months by surrendering up my thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's worked extraordinarily well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:09:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm pleased so far. And I've been doing it on two bases. One silently and the other with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,listening to some meditation CDs where they put one tone in one ear and one in the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sort of brings things up to help clear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's the, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like the Monroe Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Monroe. Sort of like Monroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Same idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is like a 10-year program and about two years into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, I find that after I do the simple one silently,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a lot more refreshing and easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'd listen to the CDs, it seems to bring out more stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm wondering which is the most advantageous to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I stick to the silent, stick to the sort of listening to the CDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it best to do a combination of both?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, which is more fruitful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's my question to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the more fruitful for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in the long term, I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think the silent ones are nice, but perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should do both of them because they seem to serve two different purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to come up, Susan, and sit where we grab you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My feeling is that they're equal in value.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're equal in value.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because the value you get out of it is the consequence of your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So your intention is the same in both directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you do prayer wheels, you would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,well, isn't that ignorant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake that thing around and your prayers are going up to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you calibrate prayer wheels, they calibrate over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the intention of one is like devoting oneself to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So then the technique becomes merely the manifestation of the intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's the intention that gives it the 510 or 520.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like the Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I tell you about the Ganges River today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:10:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, the Ganges River has a good 100 cities dump their garbage in the Ganges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the dead bodies and feces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been in that part of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And their bodies are actually floating right by you and feces, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I calibrated the Ganges, it's over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, how could a filthy river like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,People drink the Ganges water and they don't die of typhoid or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The millions of devotees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hindus over the centuries have sanctified the water of the Ganges,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Ganges is now over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges is over 500, 505, 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was around 505, 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River, so from a mechanical, chemical viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd say it's repulsive, disgusting, and probably give you a typhoid fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, food jumps 15, calibrates about 10 or 15, even 20 points higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,once you bless it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessed food calibrates higher than ordinary food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting at the bottom, you have mechanical food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates usually a little bit less than 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,tastes dead in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then food made by human energy jumps over 200 to 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then blessed food jumps up to 220.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the cook in the house, man or woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that does it out of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the family blesses it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the highest energy food there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So we always bless our kiddies' food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you bless the kiddies' food or the doggies' food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it centers, it actually goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are certain brands of cat food that calibrate below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and my cat won't eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what they do with that food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but the cat won't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I said, what does that stuff calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 190 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, I think you've answered my question,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because on that, on that basis, then I could do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could dispense with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I could dispense with the CDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because it doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, alternatively, they have some technical merit to them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that is beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They may serve a certain purpose at a certain time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everybody who gets evolved, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,checks this out, checks that out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,checks out New Ageism, chatting, channeling, psychic readings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the tarot cards, dream, dream interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's got to check it out, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out, and then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know what it is, leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, you know, you're checking it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I'm sure, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't become a master until you're educated,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and an educated master has probably been everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,trying it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He got his foot caught in the bear trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why he knows not to put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I've been trying my hand at muscle testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,since listening to your tapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and going to some of your seminars,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and one curious thing I picked up that I haven't heard of,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know whether I'm just making it up or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is in calibrating people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have found that with people deeply immersed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in a spiritual practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that I get different readings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would call the spiritual tailwind effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the deep immersion in the spiritual practice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to create a higher level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in that person than is rooted in the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and at times I see the behavior of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,at the lower level and at the higher level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering if that makes any sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, when you do kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be very specific
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,about what you're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be careful with the technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be very specific in what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I've calibrated monkeys and elephants
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to a couple of different energies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and one time I was holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the monkeys in Monkey Island
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,who were having a good time and playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Another time I was picturing monkeys out in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I was picturing an elephant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with a howdah on the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and also I learned I must use,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do image,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then I got to keep the same image comparatively,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have to be careful how I phrase the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If this person's level of consciousness is over so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So for consistency,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:16:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to keep consistent methodology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, people process information differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are more visual, some are more auditory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,some are more feeling people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I say calibrate your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,they could be picturing mother holding home-baked bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ideal mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be picture mother in a different mood
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when mother was angry at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be picturing the ideal of mother-ism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to be how mother felt, thought, felt, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to pretty much use
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the same modality predominantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm using today like conceptually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Conceptually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Conceptually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Conceptually, where is the class of hippopotamus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Conceptually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not picturing a hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See, now if I picture a hippopotamus like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I might get a different calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,than if I'm picturing the hippopotamus in the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,try to stick to the same prevailing modality
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make it too complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't get specific answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's too simple, it spends that work ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So use your own pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use my own pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okey-doke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm going to use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So while I'm answering it, I'll be happy to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Larry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Question on what we've been hearing a lot about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,over the last few months is The Passion of the Christ, the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I see where you think that would fall in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as consciousness level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention, the intention behind it is at 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His intention was 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The product, because of extensive overexposure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, to the downside, the negative torture and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know that torture goes on in prisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to witness it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought it down below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remove the torture, then you've got a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We were pressed to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If the 10 minutes of torture is removed from The Passion of the Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it jumps over 260, 300, 350, 380, 400, 395, 400, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With the torture scene in it, it calibrates over 190, 195, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So artistically, but his intention was 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was integrous in his intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the artistic side came in and I think has too much of a traumatic impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Traumatic impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But his intention was certainly at 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can sit and talk at the same time and ride a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this is going to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sign you in one second, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, when you test, when you do kinesiology testing, are you testing the consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking a calibrated level of consciousness, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking true or false.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying true or not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'm holding a number in mind and I say, this calibrates over like I just did, you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure that the thoughts and the emotions are calibrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure that the thoughts and the emotions aren't interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure that thoughts and the emotions of the person aren't interfering
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with, or your thoughts and emotions aren't interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, that has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked the fatal question, Meg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She said why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no answer to the question why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It has, so thoughts and emotions don't change the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does a quirk float?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is that way, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I know that it is, then I know it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hold, actually, the explanation of advanced theoretical physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which I gave this morning, answers it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We go from the Schrodinger equations, the potentiality of a wave function,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we collapse it through the question to a new state of the universe, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By collapsing the wave function, then, we go from potentiality into the actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the consequence, then, depends on whether or not it has a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The kinesiologic test is not between yes and no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's between yes and not yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I say, this calibrates over 460, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This calibrates over 465, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she doesn't have to know what I'm holding in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because I have an audience, I verbalize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding in mind calibrates over 485, 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm holding in mind calibrates at 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell her what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, 490, 495.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell her what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only holding it silently in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was holding the intention of the guy who created Passion of the Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mal Gibson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mal Gibson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mal Gibson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I was holding, what is this man's intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This man's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over 480, 485, 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she doesn't know what I'm holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would it be better not to have a person not know what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any difference whether they know or they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, because I like to share information with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it out loud because she gets to know the answer the same time I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At other times, if it's something very, very critical,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I may check it out silently first to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's absolutely no influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you suggest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change, but I want to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I say, no one can possibly experience their own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I may not tell her that first, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say, what I'm holding in mind is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I get true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she'll say, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.14,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience your own death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're not there to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you left the theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you know what's playing on the screen, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this to your vocal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You just answered my question, and I had a few,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've come up with another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In your practices,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything, exercise, technique, method of meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that you found particularly helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for specifically working with people?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that you found particularly helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for specifically working on raising one's consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,more effective than others?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, meditation is a whole subject in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.84,0:24:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a very simple, simple one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.01,0:24:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suspicious of altered styles of breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.68,0:24:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and physiologic manipulation, hyperventilation,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.50,0:24:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one nostril, the other nostril.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, those are all distortions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are attempts at an altered state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.47,0:24:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An altered state is not the same as a spiritual state.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.86,0:24:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha training is not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.78,0:24:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as a spontaneous spiritual effulgence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.94,0:24:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are altered states of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can train it with biofeedback,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.31,0:24:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and some yoga techniques are really just attempts
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.17,0:24:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,at altered states of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.09,0:25:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A very simple way to meditate is to close your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.77,0:25:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,look straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.31,0:25:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you close your eyes and look straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see tiny little specks of light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.64,0:25:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,on the inside of the eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.68,0:25:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I close them right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like you see multicolored,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,very tiny little specks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.07,0:25:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are called phosgenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.58,0:25:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just look ahead into the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.75,0:25:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which you could do any time except when you're driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,although some people do it when they're driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.09,0:25:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and merely focus ahead on those lights in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want, you can watch your breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.00,0:25:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.28,0:25:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.19,0:25:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.67,0:25:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is 99% silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.08,0:25:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you watch images,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.08,0:25:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.17,0:25:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and you let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.74,0:26:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of the intention that's propagating them
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.92,0:26:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as you discern what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.50,0:26:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch as the thought arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.93,0:26:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see that it arises out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.85,0:26:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say if you want to visualize how it happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.25,0:26:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts are like flying fish coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.61,0:26:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.94,0:26:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shooting out of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.96,0:26:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've ever been in the Saragasso Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.16,0:26:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or I forget what sea it was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.19,0:26:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.13,0:26:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.56,0:26:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,fly out of the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.63,0:26:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and then land on the deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.58,0:26:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.53,0:26:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this fish is not causing this fish to fly out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is still and clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.75,0:26:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but out of it comes here a fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.75,0:26:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and here a fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.66,0:26:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and here a fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.79,0:26:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the way thoughts are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of focusing on the fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you focus on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.61,0:26:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just prior to the beginning of a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.16,0:27:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is a silent sea out of which the thought arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.50,0:27:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can catch the thought earlier and earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.90,0:27:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in the process of formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.33,0:27:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you a little exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.32,0:27:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that shows how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.56,0:27:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, when you're riding in a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.52,0:27:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,your eyes, you'll watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.60,0:27:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a passenger,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.93,0:27:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,your eye shoots ahead to the telephone pole,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.71,0:27:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it tracks the telephone pole,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.75,0:27:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,then it shoots the head to a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.95,0:27:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,tracks the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.78,0:27:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then it shoots the head to a house,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.75,0:27:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,tracks the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.58,0:27:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then it shoots the head to a billboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.60,0:27:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,tracks the billboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.57,0:27:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another way of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.83,0:27:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw a circle in the right front window,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.98,0:27:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.85,0:27:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrian seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.70,0:27:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.70,0:27:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.53,0:27:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrian seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.20,0:27:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you watch through this porthole.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.18,0:27:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see the things flicking by.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.90,0:27:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how those little flicking by?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.27,0:27:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not tracking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.25,0:27:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't track it, it's just foaming by.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.83,0:27:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you become attached to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.35,0:27:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you juice it for interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.05,0:27:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you get attached to it, you juice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.07,0:27:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's like in a squeezed lemon, you let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not interesting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.24,0:28:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see a dog house up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.01,0:28:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're constantly squeezing interest out of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.56,0:28:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you focus just through the side window,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.25,0:28:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,now you can't juice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.13,0:28:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to let it go as fast as it arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.89,0:28:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you learn to witness without becoming attached,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.41,0:28:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,without beginning to seek and clutch and pull
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.47,0:28:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and juice out of it, interest, excitement, novelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.70,0:28:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see that your mind is addicted to novelty
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.42,0:28:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.11,0:28:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that your thoughts are a form of entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.35,0:28:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your little private TV set in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.19,0:28:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so as you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.78,0:28:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you see you're constantly surrendering it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.63,0:28:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.41,0:28:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I be willing to surrender this to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.91,0:28:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I let go my carnivorous interest
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.99,0:28:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in eating up all these little morsels of juicy interest
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.25,0:28:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and novelty and self amusement, self aggrandizement,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.84,0:29:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and scaring myself about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.86,0:29:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and squeezing anguish and guilt and remorse
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.58,0:29:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.75,0:29:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor old Rover and how he got run over
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.31,0:29:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and how we all cried and we couldn't eat our dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.20,0:29:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.92,0:29:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,up already you know what i mean you begin to get the feelingness of surrendering this not as a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.57,0:29:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,specific conceptual form but the feelingness of letting go and you become you you merge with the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.11,0:29:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you merge with the context you become the context in which all of this is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you merge with the context you'll feel as though your mind is expanded out into space
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.73,0:29:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,at first it's like your mind is in your head but then your mind will go out and merge with the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.25,0:30:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,totality of the context then knowingness begins to resent to you belief systems that you have to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.49,0:30:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,be willing to let go so it's a presentation then one thing after another would i be willing to
