Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.15,0:40:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got a million spies out there. Are you gonna blindside them? Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.09,0:40:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our country calibrates at 421. The UN calibrates by intention at 204, operationally about 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.23,0:40:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to turn a country at 421 to the governance of a committee that calibrates at 195?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.15,0:40:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. Well, that's what I'd felt. I just wondered what your perceptions were on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.42,0:40:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the truth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.15,0:40:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the way you kill a thing is you turn it over to committee. Everybody, any businessman
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.38,0:41:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,knows that. To me, the UN is the ultimate committee. Now, you're pretty much... With
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.96,0:41:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,sovereignty goes rights, but with sovereignty also goes obligations. I think that all the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.51,0:41:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,presidents, frankly, have done what they could do. But they're not saints. They're not Mother Teresa.
