Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.17,0:45:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The voter pushes them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.40,0:45:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we supported their integrity and said, you know, we want a wonderful person that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.59,0:45:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we can love and care about and respect, every year people compliment the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.55,0:45:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the people in charge, chief governor, you did a great job, chief president, you did a great
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.98,0:45:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,job.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.98,0:45:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.98,0:45:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.98,0:45:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They take the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.98,0:45:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the critic, the critic is too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.98,0:45:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.26,0:45:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.26,0:45:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't become Walmart's without everybody hating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.19,0:45:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.19,0:45:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:46:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why my Walmart became successful because I'd call, you know, I was a friend of Sam's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.40,0:46:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and we collaborated back and forth and I calibrated his level.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.05,0:46:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, what, you know, what attracted me was that you're going to run a big company
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.63,0:46:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,based on integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.34,0:46:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Principles of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.34,0:46:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I calibrated Sam and principles of integrity at the time they calibrated about 380 when
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.17,0:46:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.17,0:46:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what are, what are the companies going to give you your money back and operate
