Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.78,0:46:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Santa Claus, other than Santa Claus, I don't know who, you know, no sooner does
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.82,0:46:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it become successful because of its integrity that it starts becoming vilified.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.82,0:46:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.17,0:46:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.17,0:46:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made Walmart successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.17,0:46:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People that bought their products.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.80,0:46:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.80,0:46:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.98,0:46:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.98,0:46:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.98,0:46:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've got the integrity of the intention, but then you got the support of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.69,0:47:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would say what our politicians need is less vilification and more support or compassion
