Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.13,0:47:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,any who's books.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.13,0:47:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.13,0:47:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.13,0:47:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should give them our compassion, our support and our help if we have helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.80,0:47:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.80,0:47:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we send them helpful suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.98,0:47:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.98,0:47:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To make their job more successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.98,0:47:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.98,0:47:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we should, you know, give more of our appreciation to these people and less
