Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.69,0:47:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.69,0:47:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It, what does it, you know, what it takes to be a critic, nothing.
