Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.26,0:57:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chorus hit me right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.07,0:57:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I read, you know, not the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.65,0:57:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, not the textbook, but the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.44,0:57:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook calibrates at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.42,0:57:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook calibrates at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.03,0:57:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook calibrates at 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.48,0:57:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.15,0:57:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it tends to polarize the ego.
