Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.05,0:57:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a different author,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.01,0:57:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because it handles the ego completely differently
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.05,0:57:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.76,0:58:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.01,0:58:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the workbook, which is one sentence a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.11,0:58:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it bypasses the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.90,0:58:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that just struck me about the genius of the Chorus,
