Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.59,0:58:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.11,0:58:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But that person as they are
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.44,0:58:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely well defended by the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.73,0:58:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're presenting spiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.51,0:58:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to a person dominated by the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.15,0:58:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're going to shake it off like a dog does water.
