Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.73,0:59:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by obtaining the workbook,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.73,0:59:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it something that you would join a...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.73,0:59:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can do the workbook on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.73,0:59:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to join a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.73,0:59:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.80,0:59:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think they tend to intellectualize sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.80,0:59:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, and they start telling you sea stories
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.80,0:59:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about, you know, they saw a guru, so-and-so,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.80,0:59:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the thing appeared in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.80,1:00:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.80,1:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So they tend to wander off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.36,1:00:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do the workbook by yourself, seriously,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.48,1:00:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's transformative.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.48,1:00:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we tested people with kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.63,1:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way I ran across it was I was using it,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.15,1:00:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna teach a course in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.28,1:00:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was giving a class in kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.44,1:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wanted some students.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.44,1:00:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we had students hanging around the clinic,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.44,1:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, come over here, give me your arm a second,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.21,1:00:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at this fluorescent light.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.21,1:00:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And these people's arm didn't go down.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.46,1:00:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's arm goes down
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.46,1:00:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look at the fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.46,1:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what have you been up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.46,1:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, we did the Chorus of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.46,1:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chorus of Miracles, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.46,1:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So then we ran some test pupils through.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.61,1:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We tested them before they did the Chorus of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.61,1:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluorescent lights make everybody go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.61,1:00:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet and low makes everybody go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.61,1:01:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain things make everybody go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.38,1:01:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We tracked these students
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.73,1:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as they went through the Chorus of Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.73,1:01:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the time they got to about less than 80,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.73,1:01:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,75, 80, 95, around in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.73,1:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd look at the fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.73,1:01:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and their arm did not go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.73,1:01:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, they were passed,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.88,1:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,now they realized,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.88,1:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.88,1:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing out there that has any power over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.88,1:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Something had incredibly changed,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.46,1:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you cannot change your kinesiologic responses
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.46,1:01:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or your acupuncture energy rhythms voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.46,1:01:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So some force or energy or transformation
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.46,1:01:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,had taken place.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.61,1:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd say bypass the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.61,1:01:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,try the Chorus of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.61,1:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.96,1:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.76,1:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you your money back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.42,1:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy the paperback edition.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.73,1:02:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having trouble grasping the source
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.73,1:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own volition and of myself
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.73,1:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for exercising free will,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.21,1:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,making choices, having intentions.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.21,1:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what your question has to do with
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.84,1:02:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.84,1:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.84,1:02:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.53,1:02:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.53,1:02:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.53,1:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually a consequence of the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.84,1:02:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,People were asking me about meditation,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.84,1:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I forgot to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.84,1:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual will doesn't change from instant to instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.03,1:02:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The content of consciousness constantly shifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.19,1:02:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But your spiritual will,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.19,1:02:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which is your committed intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.19,1:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that does not change from moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.19,1:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spiritual will does not shift instant by instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.63,1:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Choice shifts instant by instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.63,1:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But your intention, your spiritual will,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.82,1:03:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the way you set the rudder,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.82,1:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you set your course on the compass,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.71,1:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't shift from second to second.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.78,1:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You go up a little bit on the way this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.78,1:03:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you go up a little bit of the way this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.78,1:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but the compass is already set.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.78,1:03:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's your spiritual will,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.78,1:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your intention, your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.78,1:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes the spiritual pathway work.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.78,1:03:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why there's 10,000 ways to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.78,1:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because intention is so powerful,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.78,1:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,rotating prayer wheels, burning candles,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.46,1:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting cross-legged, breathing in funny ways,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.42,1:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all of that helps because of the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.38,1:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In a deep meditation,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.38,1:03:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I experience what's your spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.38,1:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other times I experience and witness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.38,1:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,reactions within myself from lower states of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.38,1:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.38,1:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower states of consciousness. Agar.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.38,1:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.38,1:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Frustration.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.38,1:04:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I struggle with where the volition is in me
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.38,1:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a different choice, to raise that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.38,1:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you want to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.38,1:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we don't have enough time today
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.98,1:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to go into the details of transcending the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.98,1:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the positionalities,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.19,1:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the things that arise in the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.32,1:04:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like you say, anger or smay or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.61,1:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are the automatic consequence of perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.61,1:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of how you're seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.61,1:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So your problem is not anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.61,1:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem is how you're seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.61,1:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.53,1:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you ask, the miracle, what is the miracle?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.53,1:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A miracle is asking the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.53,1:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to reconsexualize it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.96,1:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that you see it differently,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.96,1:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you see there isn't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.96,1:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only how you were seeing it, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.34,1:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right and wrong, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.34,1:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I ask for that to be released, and it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.34,1:05:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask for a transformation of...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.46,1:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask the Holy Spirit to replace your perception
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.46,1:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with truth, which means you want God to,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.46,1:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the form of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.46,1:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to recontextualize it so you see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.46,1:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you see it differently, there isn't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.46,1:05:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so I ask for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.46,1:05:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just choose that or have the intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.46,1:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get more sophisticated in your spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.46,1:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.82,1:05:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can begin to do that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.82,1:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you hit a blind spot, you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.86,1:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.86,1:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hate this guy, and I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.86,1:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get off it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.86,1:05:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the way I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.59,1:05:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you ask God for help to see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.59,1:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.88,1:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you see, like I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.61,1:06:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,right and wrong, people get indignant,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.61,1:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,moralistic and politics and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.86,1:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of how you're seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.25,1:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I started out today
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.25,1:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with a scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.25,1:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I said everything there is serving something below it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.25,1:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the same time serving something above it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.25,1:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so that learning how to be a good thief
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.88,1:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is a step up from starving to death in poverty.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.88,1:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a pickpocket, Ferris, I was a good one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.88,1:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The other people lay around in poverty, not me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.23,1:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.09,1:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get farther ahead, you can let that go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.71,1:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can start out for survival, cutting corners,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.71,1:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but then your intention is to transcend that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.00,1:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one inspires that which is below it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.00,1:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and serves as an example.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.13,1:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to survive, you first have to get off the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.13,1:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So the so-called gangster robsters,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.21,1:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,robsters, robsters, what are they, robsters?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.28,1:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.51,1:07:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gangster robsters, from ethics and morality,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.01,1:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we say, isn't that awful?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.98,1:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what they're saying to you is,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.98,1:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if you folks are starving to death and lay there in apathy,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.98,1:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I'm going to be a millionaire
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.98,1:07:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and show you how to do it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.90,1:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's selling nonintegrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.90,1:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a way for an integrous purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.90,1:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you say it's just greed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.90,1:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just more than greed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.36,1:07:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's got the energy of pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.53,1:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.21,1:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing, he becomes integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.21,1:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He starts his own company.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.21,1:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see some of these rap stars
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.21,1:07:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that started out with nothing but vulgarity and obscenity.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.21,1:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they got their own record company.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.50,1:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're signing contracts,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.50,1:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're becoming ordinary businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.50,1:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So they rise out of the gutter and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.50,1:08:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,look, be like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.69,1:08:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a few bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.69,1:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wallow there in self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.69,1:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being the weak victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.76,1:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the hell up and fight for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.36,1:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can put them down, say they're vulgar and obscene,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.52,1:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but to the people below them,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.52,1:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they're inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.52,1:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.52,1:08:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we put down is inspirational
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.84,1:08:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to somebody that's really at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.84,1:08:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole country is,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.84,1:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could get them up to the level of a rap star,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.84,1:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't have to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.07,1:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have the energy to feed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.07,1:08:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The food is right there,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.07,1:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can't lift their arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.07,1:08:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at their arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.07,1:08:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all wasted.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.07,1:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.85,1:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And their brain has deteriorated with age.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.85,1:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even know where their mouth is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.94,1:08:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You better to be a rap star, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.72,1:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one of us then serves in some way,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.72,1:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and that gets us off the polarity of judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.75,1:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.75,1:09:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what the Course in Miracles does,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.75,1:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is it recontextualizes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.75,1:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.77,1:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you think he's a bad man.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.77,1:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you where he was.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.77,1:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll show you where he is now,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.77,1:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll show you where he'll be in the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.77,1:09:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Christmas past,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.77,1:09:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there's Christmas present,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.77,1:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's going to be Christmas future.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.77,1:09:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So my prediction is that today's vulgar rap star,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.97,1:09:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if he doesn't go down the tubes completely with drugs,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.97,1:09:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,will become tomorrow's business man, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.97,1:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He will become progressively integrous, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.97,1:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the consciousness level of mankind keeps going up,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.97,1:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has to pull us all up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.97,1:09:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And now your rap star is saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.73,1:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,look, I did what I had to do to get where I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.73,1:09:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look where I am, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.73,1:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Got to respect me for what I did.
